This package contains a localization library for Prison and its modules.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LocaleManager
    Provides localization support for a particular Module.
    Localizable
    Represents an object which has the potential to be localized in one of multiple languages and returned as a string.

Package tech.mcprison.prison.localization Description

This package contains a localization library for Prison and its modules.

It is the Rosetta library by Max Ronance. It has been adapted to work with Prison by Faizaan Datoo. It is licensed under the New BSD License, which is found in the LICENSE.txt file in this package.

1.0
